    <p>Do­na­tion via PayNow</p>
    <p>UEN: T11CC0007D</p>
    <p>In the ref­er­ence num­ber field, in­di­cate your NRIC/FIN and con­tact num­ber for tax ex­emp­tion.</p>
    <p>If send­ing a cheque, make it out to “SPMF“or “The Straits Times School Pocket Money Fund“and send it to: The Straits Times School Pocket Money Fund, 1000 Toa Payoh North, News Cen­tre, Sin­ga­pore 318994. In­clude the fol­low­ing in­for­ma­tion on the back of the cheque: For in­di­vid­ual donors, in­di­cate name, NRIC/FIN, con­tact num­ber and ad­dress.</p>
    <p>For cor­po­rate donors, in­di­cate com­pany name, UEN, con­tact per­son, con­tact num­ber and ad­dress. All do­na­tions are el­i­gi­ble for tax de­duc­tion of 2.5 times.</p>
    <p>Read­ers can also do­nate via the Giv­ing.sg link: www.giv­ing.sg/ web/the-straits-times-schoolpock­et-money-fund</p>
    <p>To do­nate on a monthly ba­sis, visit www.spmf.org.sg/ how-to-do­nate</p>


